Fleet says names McQuade vice chairman . Fleet Financial Group said it named Eugene McQuade its vice chairman and chief financial officer . McQuade , 48 , had been executive vice president and chief financial officer at the company . He will continue to lead Fleet ' s finance division , where he is responsible for the bank ' s investment and residential portfolios , among other things , the company said . McQuade will report directly to the company ' s chairman and chief executive , Terrence Murray , Fleet added . 
